{"tid":2279410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊潤雄聲稱再有教師涉「宣揚港獨」受查　正研究修改法律授權教育局可對教師釘牌、停薪及扣薪","createTime":"2020-11-09T18:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T13:41:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f17e2a00bb14f927787bde7ac4c42324b0a64199","tid":2279410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T18:48:33.000Z","msg":"繼九龍塘宣道小學一名教師被指散播港獨而遭釘牌後，教育局不遺餘力「追殺」被藍絲投訴的教師。教育局長楊潤雄透露，正處理兩名教師嚴重專業失德個案，首次披露其中一人同樣涉及「宣揚港獨」。楊潤雄更趁機增加對付教師的手段，正研究修改法律，授權教育局可對教師釘牌一段時間、停薪及扣薪等處分。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄在新一期《亞洲週刊》題為「香港教育界亟待撥亂反正」的專訪中指，教育局仍在跟進60宗有關教師專業操守的投訴，當中有兩宗比較嚴重，包括「一個宣揚港獨」，又指該教師「專業能力也有問題，課堂準備不足，對教學的資料沒有核實和求證，明顯沒有對學生負責任」。另一個案涉中學教材，「我們覺得很有問題」。他又指，有些老師不合作，教育局需花更多工夫調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/WGMTRIP2CZCGJBYB2XSCSXL56A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FWGMTRIP2CZCGJBYB2XSCSXL56A%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=55695964\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FWGMTRIP2CZCGJBYB2XSCSXL56A%2F&h=88bcb27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/WGMTRIP2CZCGJBYB2XSCSXL56A/</a>"},{"pid":"778364d2c4be2c825d03bfd0eac9c9f538bdaa4b","tid":2279410,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"好快引入支那老師、校長"},{"pid":"526120a7091cba70520df00ea03319916bbc2748","tid":2279410,"uid":83582,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T18:55:25.000Z","msg":"新制裁名單大熱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a3abbc4d0c61d462524d35b0a0bc4c043bdd48","tid":2279410,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T18:55:42.000Z","msg":"搏制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959b30d868055ccdbbed6715f521c551001cae95","tid":2279410,"uid":383914,"like":0,"disl